data.description: Welcome to this cute cape cod home with hardwood flooring and light filled rooms. The open floor plan begins with the comfortable living room and adjoining dining room with a sliding glass door leading to the composite deck (installed 2020) overlooking the fenced yard. The well equipped kitchen includes Samsung stainless refrigerator and gas range, Fridgidaire stainless dishwasher, granite counter tops and plenty of storage. The primary bedroom can be found on the first or second floor with two bedrooms on the first floor with wall to wall carpeting and share the hall bathroom. The third bedroom suite is the entire second floor with its own full bath and generous closet space. The lower level recreation room provides an additional family gathering space and is ideal for a game room, exercise room and hobbies. The laundry is found here as well. The spacious two car garage has a newer door and opener (2022) and the furnace, A/C and hot water tank were installed in 2015.
